  <description><![CDATA[<p>This unescorted cycle tour gives you total freedom to discover the picturesque and vast River Danube from Vienna to Budapest. The riverbanks are brimming with historical culture, castles, forests and towns– summer is a beautiful time to explore this medieval trade route, which was once integral to the Roman Empire. The route takes you through Austria, Slovakia and Hungary before your final stop in Budapest.</p>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-austria/treasures-of-the-danube-vienna-to-budapest#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-austria/treasures-of-the-danube-vienna-to-budapest#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-austria/treasures-of-the-danube-vienna-to-budapest#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-austria/treasures-of-the-danube-vienna-to-budapest#Hotels">Hotels </a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-austria/treasures-of-the-danube-vienna-to-budapest#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
